  "page": "Lord Dondarrion (father of Simon)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dondarrion\" title=\"House Dondarrion\"><img alt=\"House Dondarrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/50px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/75px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/100px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Dondarrion</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dondarrion\" title=\"House Dondarrion\"><img alt=\"House Dondarrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/50px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/75px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/100px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Blackhaven\" title=\"Lord of Blackhaven\">Lord of Blackhaven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Dondarrion\" title=\"House Dondarrion\">House Dondarrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Marcher</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/61_AC\" title=\"61 AC\">61&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Simon Dondarrion\">Simon Dondarrion</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Dondarrion</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Blackhaven\" title=\"Blackhaven\">Blackhaven</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dondarrion\" title=\"House Dondarrion\">House Dondarrion</a> during the early reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if this is the same individual as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Harmon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Harmon Dondarrion\">Harmon Dondarrion</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Dondarrion_(father_of_Simon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54&#160;AC</a>, Lord Dondarrion hosted King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> and Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Blackhaven\" title=\"Blackhaven\">Blackhaven</a> during their return from a <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">royal progress</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. The royal couple stayed longer than they had intended but left immediately on <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragonback</a> when they learned their mother, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a>, was dying at <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>By <a href=\"/index.php/61_AC\" title=\"61 AC\">61&#160;AC</a>, he was succeeded as Lord of Blackhaven by his son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Simon Dondarrion\">Simon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Dondarrion_(father_of_Simon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Birth, Death, and Betrayal Under King Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne - Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Blackhaven\" title=\"Lord of Blackhaven\">Lord of Blackhaven</a> </b><br />?–<a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/61_AC\" title=\"61 AC\">61&#160;AC</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Dondarrion\" title